      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a reliable choice for someone looking for a solid driver at a lower price point. The exterior shows noticeable signs of age, including several larger scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some minor staining, though all controls are functional. It has been regularly serviced, but prospective buyers should expect upcoming maintenance items typical for a car of this age and mileage.",
